firstPaint.summary: The time immediately before the first paint occurred

connectEnd.summary: The time immediately after the user agent finished establishing the connection to the server to retrieve the document

connectStart.summary: The time immediately before the user agent started establishing the connection to the server to retrieve the document

domainLookupEnd.summary: The time immidiately after the user agent finishes the domain name lookup for the document

domainLookupStart.summary: The time immediately before the user agent started the domain name lookup for the document

domComplete.summary: The time immediately before the user agent set the document's readiness to complete

domContentLoadedEventEnd.summary: The time immediately after the document's DOMContentLoaded event completed

domContentLoadedEventStart.summary: The time immediately before the user agent fired the DOMContentLoaded event

domInteractive.summary: The time immidiately before the user agent set the document's readiness to interactive

domLoading.summary: The time immidiately before the user agent set the document's readiness to loading

fetchStart.summary: The time immediately before the user agent checks caches for resources OR starts fetching resources

loadEventEnd.summary: The time the load event for the document completed

loadEventStart.summary: The time immediately before the load event was fired for the document

requestStart.summary: The time immediately before the user agent started requesting the document from the server

responseStart.summary: The time immediately after the user agent received the first byte of the server's response to the document request
